# Code quality

- After every code change: `npm run lint` (mandatory — see `lint-verification.mdc`)
- TypeScript strict; no unjustified `any`
- Arrow functions only (`arrow-functions.mdc`)
- For AI infra TypeScript: `npm run typecheck:ai`
- For major changes: `npm run build`
- Prefer existing patterns in `src/components` and `.ai/lib`
